<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Candidate Profile Updated - Review Required</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%);">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); padding: 40px 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: #1E293B; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3); box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);">
          
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F6 0%, #8B5CF6 50%, #06B6D4 100%); padding: 50px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <div style="width: 90px; height: 90px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4); line-height: 90px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
                <span style="font-size: 45px;">üîî</span>
              </div>
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Profile Update Alert</h1>
              <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500;">Admin Review Required</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 50px 40px;">
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 100%); border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6; padding: 25px; margin: 0 0 35px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="color: #93C5FD; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 700;">
                  ‚ö° Action Required
                </p>
                <p style="color: #DBEAFE; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;">
                  A candidate has updated their profile and it requires your review and approval before going live.
                </p>
              </div>

              <!-- Candidate Info Card -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%); border: 2px solid #3B82F6; border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 35px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);">
                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 15px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);">
                      <span style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 13px; display: block; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Candidate</span>
                      <span style="color: #3B82F6; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; display: block;">{{candidateName}}</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 15px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);">
                      <span style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 13px; display: block; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Event</span>
                      <span style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; display: block;">{{eventTitle}}</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 15px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);">
                      <span style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 13px; display: block; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Updated At</span>
                      <span style="color: #F1F5F9; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; display: block;">{{formatDateTime updatedAt}}</span>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 15px 0;">
                      <span style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 13px; display: block; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Status</span>
                      <div style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F59E0B 0%, #EF4444 100%); color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 25px; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);">
                        ‚è≥ PENDING REVIEW
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </div>

              {{#if changedFieldsList}}
              <!-- Changed Fields -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 100%); border: 2px solid #F59E0B; border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 35px;">
                <h3 style="color: #FCD34D; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 20px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">üìù Fields Changed</h3>
                <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #FDE68A; font-size: 14px; line-height: 2;">
                  {{#each changedFieldsList}}
                  <li style="font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-weight: 600;">{{this}}</li>
                  {{/each}}
                </ul>
              </div>
              {{else if changedFields}}
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 100%); border: 2px solid #F59E0B; border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 35px;">
                <h3 style="color: #FCD34D; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 15px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">üìù Fields Changed</h3>
                <p style="color: #FDE68A; margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7;">{{changedFields}}</p>
              </div>
              {{/if}}

              <!-- Important Notice -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15) 0%, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.05) 100%); border-left: 4px solid #EF4444; padding: 25px; margin-bottom: 35px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="color: #FCA5A5; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 700;">
                  ‚ö†Ô∏è Important Notice
                </p>
                <p style="color: #FED7D7; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;">
                  The candidate's profile has been automatically <strong style="color: #F87171;">unpublished</strong> and their status changed to "Profile Update Pending". They will not be visible to voters until you review and approve the changes.
                </p>
              </div>

              <p style="color: #CBD5E1; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 35px;">
                Please review the updated profile to ensure all information meets your event's standards and guidelines before approval.
              </p>

              <!-- CTA Button -->
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 35px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{reviewUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F6 0%, #8B5CF6 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 20px 60px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 17px; box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">
                      Review Profile Now ‚Üí
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Review Tips -->
              <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15) 0%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15) 100%); border-left: 4px solid #10B981; padding: 25px; margin-top: 35px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <p style="color: #6EE7B7; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px; font-weight: 700;">
                  üí° Review Tips
                </p>
                <p style="color: #A7F3D0; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7;">
                  Check that all updated information is accurate, appropriate, and follows your event guidelines. You can approve or reject the changes, or provide feedback to the candidate.
                </p>
              </div>

              <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 35px 0 0; font-style: italic;">
                This is an automated notification from ITFY E-Voting Platform<br>
                <strong style="color: #CBD5E1;">Event Administration Team</strong>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);">
              <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 10px;">
                <a href="{{reviewUrl}}" style="color: #3B82F6; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Admin Dashboard</a> | 
                <a href="mailto:support@itfy-evoting.com" style="color: #06B6D4; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Contact Support</a>
              </p>
              <p style="color: #64748B; font-size: 12px; margin: 10px 0 0;">
                ¬© {{formatDate currentYear}} ITFY E-Voting. All rights reserved.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>